<TEXTAREA NAME="ReplyMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">[QUOTE]Originally posted by Kaysha Soulsinger:
[B]60 CLR and ENC don't solo, but duo :b

Anyway, yes, they can handle the Goblins easy. Each Goblin will give you +1 point of faction, you need roughly 3000 or so faction points to go from max KoS to max Ally. Luckily, you can also turn in Goblin Skins and Mineral Salts that both drop in the Gobbie areas to Herald Telcha (can be found at the Chardok zone). As long as your faction is anywhere reasonable (I believe Dubious is already enough), you will get +3 points of faction for each skin/salt you turn in.
[/B][/QUOTE]

